Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上週已經要你們先讀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教材的153頁到162頁當做作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  大概就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫又在打瞌睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.24,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過這樣的事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我這也不是白當倫的朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫  烤薄餅做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  烤薄餅在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫  聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊  有點吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  你還太嫩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這題好難哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  解下一題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  試著把這道題當做人生的問題吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果同樣沒有解決而逃避掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有著無論什麼困難都能克服的力量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喚醒吧  沉睡在你心中的熾熱靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定能做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢嚓？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢嚓？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢嚓…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼頭老師在上課時受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育課？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是數學課
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數學…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,240)\fs40}超大份烤薄餅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在上課時受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒資格當老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼頭  聽說你手受傷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我幫你泡了咖啡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是順便泡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  鐮手老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  讓我拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那柚多谷也來拿點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家變成了我的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是無比幸福的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來貼身保護吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我明明是擔心你而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的擔心我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是還幫你纏了繃帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是另一回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  繃帶下面是不是很癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始上課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次關於189頁的公式進行了簡單講解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們來證明它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為教師怎麼能輸給這點小痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來替您寫黑板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被粉筆灰弄髒了  穿上白大衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可以有！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們繼續上課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,173頁的第二章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從第一個公式的證明開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在笑什麼  請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然拖了特地來幫我的學生的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說您受傷了  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣  紀美子  不能過分讓學生擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  你們看  已經快好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不痛 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透同學  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  交得晚了真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把之前的作業帶來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  手機的鈴聲忘關了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我拿給您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得怎麼這麼重  什麼時候進來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在上課  也不能交給誰來看著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好先回家了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是透家的貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓柚多谷也抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是果汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好哦  果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸好可愛啊  真是隻漂亮的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我還想摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  找到去透家的藉口了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷我也想摸個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到本人同意了  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏住黏住黏住…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.28,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你不去透家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  你回家了一趟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  第一節課沒有上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊  這種時間就該坐計程車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐的胸部好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又鬆又軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別摸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說透是很喜歡小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  不用東西來引誘也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓透你去還球吧  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊玩設施  好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下來啦  丟臉死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩啊  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說  小渚不也坐上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是當長凳坐的啦  長凳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚打電話抱歉啊  現在能接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想之前渚想要借的CD是哪張來著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就拿第二張給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在忙什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  別裝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了沒在做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說明天見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不知道什麼時候掛斷才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}\N\N\N\N\N\N痊\N愈\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:18.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N於\N是\N於\N是\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把積攢的詩寫完啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴿子模仿得好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  瘦了一點點！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺腿也稍微細了一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  小渚的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏居然有顆痣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別趁機偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近的百貨店裏面好像開了一家新的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的超大份烤薄餅好像很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得你這麼有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這個禮拜六去怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哎  那我就從早上開始一直空著肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不好好吃早飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯  快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是幾樓呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是假日好擠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…是那個被稱為「FLAG」的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於已經瘦掉點的我來說  是不會被淘汰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  給我記住了  我爬樓梯還不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚  你好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  所有的準備都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  是四位客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請往這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員小姐的制服真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  把衣服疊好放在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這菜單做得真細緻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好不用排隊就可以進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要喝什麼飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏紅茶的種類也好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以點一壺叫她們拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚你喝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之比起紅茶來  我想先喝水…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大杯的水…拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請給我們水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就點這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超大份烤薄餅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼好不容易來一次  那我就點這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就點不同的東西  然後交換著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我們要點單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  現在就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是透同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏打工哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說柚多谷也在這裏打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不是什麼時候都在一起的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  稍微讓開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是透的同學吧   謝謝你平時一直照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  都是她照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透同學在一年級的女生裏是很受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說她很帥氣又可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同學經常提到她  還會介紹給老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:57.13,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我要超大份烤薄餅兩個  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漿果蛋糕一個  抹茶蛋糕一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉嶺和熱的錫蘭高地奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加阿薩姆紅茶兩杯  一份加檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  請讓我和您確認下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份烤薄餅兩個  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漿果蛋糕一個  抹茶蛋糕一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉嶺和熱的錫蘭高地奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加阿薩姆紅茶兩杯  一份加檸檬對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好能幹的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  十分抱歉  現在滿座了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待時間啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人真是十分抱歉  再過二十分鐘左右就有位子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困擾啊  我現在就想喝到熱熱的紅茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷我不知道能不能等得了二十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一小會兒你可以等的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豐～大～人～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員不能揪人臉的  美寶蓮好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就乖乖給我坐在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓她打擾透和前輩們用餐就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要把柚多谷安排到比較遠的位置才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美寶蓮  你有什麼瞞著我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你突然說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又把胸弄小了啊  這件制服一眼就看出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要來也不要挑店裏最忙的時候來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用給你服務也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天柚多谷是來支援美寶蓮的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功能表功能表  點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.99,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要點些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要份…本日的紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是工作日才能喝到的紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤薄餅蛋糕快點來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過去好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大份烤薄餅也快來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種店慢慢地品味紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種大人的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人嗎  我還真不想當大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直待在學校裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想快點長大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人…我可以成為大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透還真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  居然在這個地方偶遇你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺這都是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說話  柚多谷做了什麼壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  她現在在咀嚼中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們初中就是同一所學校的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷和美寶蓮也是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是美寶蓮不在  她就不能妨礙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員很忙真是悲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚多谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  店員小姐  咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來妨礙你了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你工作怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了換班時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了  柚多谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你們慢慢享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透…學校再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透的班級也蠻有趣的  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個活潑的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升上二年級以後還能在一個班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久  二號線電車就要靠站了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要乘坐這班電車的請準備好上車了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想嘗嘗小倫和烤薄餅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次在家裏也試著做做烤薄餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比這好吃的東西我認為沒那麼容易做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事  我有自信比這家店可以做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說過不要妨礙透同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤薄餅好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了不要在忙的時候來店裏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…美寶蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聽好了  只有在店裏不忙的時候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回復一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拉長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  美寶蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那制服很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意圖太簡單易懂了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  柚多谷和美寶蓮都好好表現了一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集我們也還會好好表現的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集A頻道  +Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在繪馬上祈願」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：繪馬即為在神社祈禱或者還願時掛在寺社內繪畫木板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頻道就保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是OVA啊
